sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as Training Operator Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as Training Operator Controller
    participant Scheduler as Gang Scheduler<br/>(Volcano/scheduler-plugins)
    participant Master as Master Pod<br/>23456/TCP
    participant Worker as Worker Pods
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Worker: Flow 1: Training Job Creation
    User->>API: POST PyTorchJob CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>Webhook: ValidatingWebhook Request<br/>mTLS
    Webhook->>API: Validation Response<br/>Accepted/Rejected
    API-->>User: Job Created

    Note over User,Worker: Flow 2: Job Reconciliation Loop
    API->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>PyTorchJob Created<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create PodGroup<br/>for Gang Scheduling<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Master Pod<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Worker Pods<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Master Service<br/>23456/TCP<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>for Job Isolation<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token

    Scheduler->>API: Schedule Pods<br/>Gang Scheduling
    API->>Master: Start Master Pod
    API->>Worker: Start Worker Pods

    Note over User,Worker: Flow 3: Distributed Training Communication
    Worker->>Master: Connect to Master<br/>23456/TCP Framework Protocol
    Worker->>Worker: P2P Communication<br/>Various/TCP Framework Protocol
    Master-->>Worker: Training Coordination
    Worker-->>Master: Gradient Updates

    Note over User,Worker: Flow 4: Status Updates
    Master->>Controller: Status Update<br/>(via API watch)
    Controller->>API: Update Job Status<br/>TLS 1.2+ ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>User: Job Status: Running/Succeeded/Failed

    Note over User,Worker: Flow 5: Metrics Collection
    Prom->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
    Controller-->>Prom: Operator & Job Metrics
